<view class="page">

  <!-- U1 · 顶部金色滚动进度条（CHG-20260428-02 U1） -->
  <view class="scroll-progress" aria-hidden="true">
    <view class="scroll-progress__fill" style="width: {{progress}}%"></view>
  </view>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <poster-sky tone="light" min-height="880rpx">
    <view class="hero">
      <view class="hero-left">
        <view class="hero-meta-row">
          <view class="mono eyebrow">DCT · VOL.02 · 2026.04.25</view>
          <!-- F5 · 倒计时 chip（CHG-20260428-03 F5） -->
          <view wx:if="{{daysLeftLabel}}" class="mono countdown-chip">{{daysLeftLabel}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="serif title">
          <view>六星</view>
          <view>之路</view>
        </view>
        <view class="subline">
          <view class="star-bullet star-gold"></view>
          <text class="subline-text">目标管理与坚持哲学</text>
        </view>
        <view class="subline-dash">——写给学术追梦人的漫谈</view>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-portrait-wrap">
        <image class="hero-portrait"
               src="/assets/gao-portrait.jpg"
               mode="aspectFill"
               lazy-load="true"
               binderror="onImgError" />
        <view class="hero-portrait-fade"></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- F1 · 报名状态横幅（CHG-20260428-03 F1） -->
    <view wx:if="{{regStatus}}" class="reg-banner reg-banner--{{regStatus}}" catchtap="goForm">
      <view class="reg-banner__dot"></view>
      <view class="reg-banner__text">{{regBannerText}}</view>
    </view>

    <!-- speaker card -->
    <view class="speaker-wrap {{regStatus ? 'speaker-wrap--with-banner' : ''}}">
      <view class="speaker-card">
        <view class="speaker-avatar">
          <image src="/assets/gao-avatar-poster.png"
                 mode="aspectFill"
                 class="speaker-avatar-img"
                 lazy-load="true"
                 binderror="onImgError" />
        </view>
        <view class="speaker-info">
          <view class="speaker-name">
            <text>高晓蓉</text>
            <text class="speaker-title"> 教授</text>
          </view>
          <view class="speaker-bio">
            <view>西南交通大学光电工程研究所</view>
            <view>马拉松六星跑者 "Six Star Finisher"</view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </poster-sky>

  <dct-origin-story />

  <!-- OPENING PITCH -->
  <view class="section section-top">
    <view class="serif opening-title">
      <view>在学术里保持严谨，</view>
      <view>在生活中追求热爱。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="opening-body">
      DCT 第二期，我们很荣幸邀请到高晓蓉教授来到客厅，与我们分享她关于<text class="opening-accent">目标、坚持与多重人生角色</text>的思考。
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- THREE POINTS · CHG-02 U4 -->
  <view class="section">
    <view class="mono section-kicker">SHE WILL SHARE</view>
    <view class="serif section-title">从真实经历出发，三个侧面</view>
    <view class="points">
      <view class="point-card" wx:for="{{points}}" wx:key="num">
        <!-- left icon container -->
        <view class="point-icon">
          <!-- lanes: 三条横线 + 三个金点 -->
          <view wx:if="{{item.icon === 'lanes'}}" class="ico ico-lanes">
            <view class="ico-lane"><view class="ico-dot"></view></view>
            <view class="ico-lane"><view class="ico-dot"></view></view>
            <view class="ico-lane"><view class="ico-dot"></view></view>
          </view>
          <!-- footprint: 两组脚印 -->
          <view wx:elif="{{item.icon === 'footprint'}}" class="ico ico-footprint">
            <view class="ico-foot ico-foot--l1"></view>
            <view class="ico-foot ico-foot--r1"></view>
            <view class="ico-foot ico-foot--l2"></view>
            <view class="ico-foot ico-foot--r2"></view>
          </view>
          <!-- compass: 圆 + 内嵌指针 -->
          <view wx:elif="{{item.icon === 'compass'}}" class="ico ico-compass">
            <view class="ico-compass-needle"></view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="point-body">
          <view class="point-head">
            <view class="serif point-title">{{item.title}}</view>
            <view class="mono point-num">{{item.num}}</view>
          </view>
          <view class="point-sub">{{item.sub}}</view>
          <view class="point-text">{{item.body}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- CLOSING LINE -->
  <view class="section">
    <view class="closing">
      <view class="closing-text">
        这不仅是一场成功经验分享，更是<text class="serif closing-accent">一封写给所有学术追梦人的信</text>——关于如何在生活里，持续相信、持续行动，持续成为自己想成为的人。
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- EVENT INFO · CHG-02 U7：用 :not(:last-child)::after 替代独立 sep 节点 -->
  <view class="section">
    <view class="mono section-kicker">WHEN · WHERE · HOW</view>
    <view class="info-card">
      <view class="info-row" wx:for="{{infoRows}}" wx:key="label">
        <view class="mono info-label">{{item.label}}</view>
        <view class="info-col">
          <view class="info-value">{{item.value}}</view>
          <view class="info-sub">{{item.sub}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- SEASONAL MENU · CHG-02 U5 -->
  <view class="section">
    <view class="mono section-kicker">EARLY SUMMER · LIMITED</view>
    <view class="menu-card">
      <view class="serif menu-title">初夏季节限定</view>
      <view class="menu-sub">Mulberry season, from Panzhihua</view>
      <!-- U5 · 不含正餐 chip -->
      <view class="menu-chip">
        <view class="menu-chip__icon"></view>
        <text>本期不含正餐 · 建议先吃晚饭再来</text>
      </view>
      <view class="menu-sep"></view>
      <view class="menu-list">
        <view class="menu-row" wx:for="{{menu}}" wx:key="name">
          <view class="star-bullet star-brown"></view>
          <view class="serif menu-name">{{item.name}}</view>
          <view class="mono menu-tag">{{item.tag}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="menu-foot">
        <view>担心甜品负担也可以打包带走。</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- WHAT IS DCT -->
  <view class="section">
    <view class="dct-head">
      <image src="/assets/logo.png"
             class="dct-logo"
             lazy-load="true"
             binderror="onImgError" />
      <view class="dct-head-text">
        <view class="mono section-kicker">WHAT IS DCT ?</view>
        <view class="serif dct-head-title">认真地胡思乱想</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="dct-tagline">——用科学的态度，聊天马行空的奇思妙想</view>
    <view class="dct-latin">Doctors' Crazy Thinking · Dog, Chef & Therapist</view>
    <view class="dct-body">
      <view>一个家庭学术沙龙。在绩效逻辑之外，留一块真诚分享、自由交流、严肃思考的精神自留地。</view>
      <view class="dct-body-line2">在客厅里聊学术，也聊生活；聊目标，也聊热爱。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="serif dct-invite">期待和你一起，建设这块精神自留地。</view>
  </view>

  <!-- RULES ENTRY -->
  <view class="section">
    <view class="rules-entry" bindtap="goDetail" hover-class="tap-hover" aria-label="查看活动须知与吧规">
      <view class="rules-entry-text">
        <view class="rules-entry-title">活动须知与 DCT · 吧规</view>
        <view class="rules-entry-sub">报名前建议先读一下</view>
      </view>
      <view class="chevron"></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <view class="cta-wrap">
    <button class="cta"
            bindtap="goForm"
            hover-class="cta-hover"
            aria-label="{{ctaAriaLabel}}">
      <view class="star-bullet star-cta"></view>
      <text class="cta-text">{{ctaText}}</text>
      <view class="star-bullet star-cta"></view>
    </button>
    <view class="cta-sub">
      我们会根据学科背景与意愿综合筛选，<text class="cta-sub-accent">24 小时内回复</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- U2 · 吸底浮动 CTA（CHG-20260428-02 U2，position: fixed per pasted note） -->
  <view class="sticky-cta {{stickyVisible ? 'is-visible' : ''}}" catchtap="goForm" aria-hidden="{{!stickyVisible}}">
    <view class="sticky-cta__inner">
      <view class="sticky-cta__info">
        <view class="mono sticky-cta__kicker">VOL.02 · 04.25</view>
        <view class="sticky-cta__price">
          <text class="sticky-cta__num">88</text>
          <text class="sticky-cta__unit">元/位</text>
          <text class="sticky-cta__hint">含甜品+酒</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="sticky-cta__btn">
        <view class="star-bullet star-cta sticky-cta__star"></view>
        <text>{{ctaTextShort}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

</view>
